{
  "version": 2,
  "name": "ConcentricTunnel",
  "description": "Concentric polygon rings expanding outward from the centre — decomposed from the legacy `ConcentricTunnelGenerator` Rust struct into the curated primitive library.\n\n`node.polygon_shape` produces one polygon outline (Circle = 64-gon, Triangle, Square, Pentagon, or Hexagon — the legacy Star variant is removed); `node.concentric_outlines` stacks K=16 scaled copies driven by an `expansion` scalar so the stack drifts outward over time and new rings emerge from the centre at radius 0; `node.render_lines` draws the stack with the legacy line + dot semantics.\n\nThe legacy three-state `clip_trigger_mode` is restored as the outer-card `trigger_mode` param. With `clip_trigger` on:\n- **Shape**: each retrigger cycles the polygon through [3, 4, 5, 6, 8, 12]; no new ring spawn.\n- **Spawn**: each retrigger spawns a new ring from the centre; shape stays at the user's `shape` selection.\n- **Both**: both.\n\nShape cycling is done entirely in the graph: `node.clip_trigger_index` (modulus 6) advances on each retrigger; `mux_cycle_sides` maps that index through the [3, 4, 5, 6, 8, 12] table; `mux_final_n_sides` switches between the user-selected `mux_n_sides.out` and the cycled value based on `clip_trigger × mode_shape_enable`. The same `clip_trigger × mode_*_enable` gating pattern feeds `spawn_gate.b` for ring-spawn. `polygon_shape.clip_trigger` is left off — its internal cycle is unused because the mode-gated external cycle replaces it (and only one ClipTriggerCycle is in play, inside `clip_trigger_index`).\n\nMux inputs are wired through explicit `node.value` constants so the graph editor shows every input that drives the mux selection — the inline-param shortcut on mux_scalar was reverted in favour of visual clarity (matches the Lissajous precedent). Legacy outer-card `scale` is renamed to `ring_spacing` with a different scale; old projects will need to retune.",
  "presetMetadata": {
    "id": "ConcentricTunnel",
    "displayName": "Concentric Tunnel",
    "category": "Procedural",
    "oscPrefix": "concentricTunnel",
    "legacyDiscriminant": 5,
    "available": true,
    "isLineBased": true,
    "params": [
      {
        "id": "shape",
        "name": "Shape",
        "min": 0.0,
        "max": 4.0,
        "defaultValue": 0.0,
        "wholeNumbers": true,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F0",
        "oscSuffix": "shape",
        "valueLabels": ["Circle", "Triangle", "Square", "Pentagon", "Hexagon"]
      },
      {
        "id": "line",
        "name": "Line",
        "min": 0.0005,
        "max": 0.03,
        "defaultValue": 0.008,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F4",
        "oscSuffix": "line"
      },
      {
        "id": "rate",
        "name": "Rate",
        "min": 0.0,
        "max": 4.0,
        "defaultValue": 2.0,
        "wholeNumbers": true,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F0",
        "oscSuffix": "rate",
        "valueLabels": ["1/4", "1/2", "1", "2", "4"]
      },
      {
        "id": "ring_spacing",
        "name": "Ring Spacing",
        "min": 0.05,
        "max": 0.3,
        "defaultValue": 0.12,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F2",
        "oscSuffix": "ringSpacing"
      },
      {
        "id": "clip_trigger",
        "name": "Clip Trigger",
        "min": 0.0,
        "max": 1.0,
        "defaultValue": 0.0,
        "wholeNumbers": false,
        "isToggle": true,
        "formatString": "F0",
        "oscSuffix": "clipTrigger"
      },
      {
        "id": "trigger_mode",
        "name": "Trigger Mode",
        "min": 0.0,
        "max": 2.0,
        "defaultValue": 2.0,
        "wholeNumbers": true,
        "isToggle": false,
        "formatString": "F0",
        "oscSuffix": "triggerMode",
        "valueLabels": ["Shape", "Spawn", "Both"]
      }
    ],
    "paramAliases": [
      { "old": "scale", "new": "ring_spacing" },
      { "old": "clip_trigger_mode", "new": "trigger_mode" }
    ],
    "bindings": [
      { "id": "shape", "label": "Shape", "defaultValue": 0.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "mux_n_sides", "param": "selector" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "line", "label": "Line", "defaultValue": 0.008,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "render", "param": "edge_thickness" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "rate", "label": "Rate", "defaultValue": 2.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "mux_ring_freq", "param": "selector" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "ring_spacing", "label": "Ring Spacing", "defaultValue": 0.12,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "stack", "param": "ring_spacing" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "clip_trigger", "label": "Clip Trigger", "defaultValue": 0.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "shape_active", "param": "a" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "clip_trigger", "label": "Clip Trigger", "defaultValue": 0.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "spawn_active", "param": "a" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "trigger_mode", "label": "Trigger Mode", "defaultValue": 2.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "mode_shape_enable", "param": "selector" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "trigger_mode", "label": "Trigger Mode", "defaultValue": 2.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "mode_spawn_enable", "param": "selector" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } }
    ],
    "skipMode": { "kind": "never" }
  },
  "nodes": [
